XPX@xparty.name: XPX

It operates with a market maker where buy orders are placed for the same amount of XPX sold. There are no team-allocated XPX tokens, no marketing budget, just 100% of the supply listed on the market 📊. XPX will consistently have reward pools 💎 but will never serve as the reward token itself. To maintain its value, XPX employs a strategy where every XPX token sold is used to buy back the token. When the sell order is gone, XPX starts ratcheting, moving up the starting price 2% while maintaining market stabilization mechanisms that rise as well 📈. You can run this market maker by executing the 'partytime' action on maker.xpx with freecover = 0 ⚙️. The market maker targets a support level of 0.98 WAX with 62% of liquidity and an additional 10% at 0.96 WAX, and descending orders until 0.62. The weighted gap in all buy orders is calculated to be 6.6%, which is taken as fees to run the project 🔍. If you've never searched XPX under Alcor farms, you will 🌾.
